    dc:creator "Liu, Shiyu", "Liu, Tengteng", "Teng, Kaijian", "Xu, Jiasheng", "Yu, Jiazhi" ;
    dc:date "2023" ;
    dc:title "The leaf-mining genus Lyonetia Hübner from China, with descriptions of two new species (Lepidoptera: Yponomeutoidea: Lyonetiidae)" ;
    bibo:endPage "120" ;
    bibo:issue "1" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:pubDate "2023-10-17" ;
    bibo:startPage "100" ;
    bibo:volume "5357" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10012631>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10012641>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10012649>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10012653> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10012631>
    dc:description "FIGURES 7–11. Adults of Lyonetia spp. 7–8, L. (Lyonetia) clerkella: 7, female, autumnal form, Xizang, SDNU.Ent005012; 8, autumnal form, Xizang, SDNU.Ent005177; 9, L. (Lyonetia) ledi, female, SDNU.Ent001388; 10–11, L. (Lyonetia) prunifoliella: 10, female, aestival form, SDNU.Ent001251; 11, male, autumnal form, SDNU.Ent028198. Scales = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10012631/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10012641>
    dc:description "FIGURES 16–17. Male genitalia of Lyonetia spp. 16, L. (Lyonetia) clerkella: 16a, sclerotized ridge and superuncus on 8th tergite, slide no. LSY0079; 16b, lateral view, slide no. LSY0063; 17, L. (Lyonetia) prunifoliella, slide no. LSY0064: 17a, sclerotized ridge and superuncus on 8th tergite; 17b, lateral view. Scales = 200 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10012641/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10012649>
    dc:description "FIGURE 22. Female genitalia of Lyonetia (Lyonetia) prunifoliella, slide no. LM0194; 22a, sclerotized plate on ductus bursae." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10012649/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10012653>
    dc:description "FIGURES 23–30. Biology of Lyonetia spp. 23–26, L. (Lyonetiola) blasta, sp. n.: 23–25, irregular shrunken and brown leaf mines; 26, host plant Blastus pauciflorus; 27, L. (Lyonetia) clerkella, leaf mine in Prunus triloba; 28–30, L. (Lyonetia) prunifoliella: 28–29, irregular pale green and pale brown leaf mines in Prunus triloba; 30, leaf mines with alive larvae on Prunus triloba. Arrows showing the mines." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10012653/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

